   - **Digital Substrate trademarks** (logos, brand marks) are not
     licensed under either CC-BY or MIT and remain the exclusive
     property of Digital Substrate. CC-BY 4.0 §2(b) already states
     in general terms that CC licenses do not grant trademark
     rights; this notice restates it for clarity.

   - **Third-party UI screenshots** (e.g. screenshots depicting
     Visual Studio Code, JetBrains IDEs) reproduce trademarks of
     their respective owners. Their inclusion in this documentation
     is for the purpose of factual product description and use
     instruction, under the right of citation
     (Code de la propriété intellectuelle, Art. L. 122-5; equivalent
     fair-use doctrines apply in other jurisdictions). The
     trademarks remain the property of their owners; reproduction
     is permitted within the scope of this documentation only.

